{"tid":1551100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"謝偉俊：與其為「少少野」爭拗，不如醒覺搞下環保仲好啦","createTime":"2019-09-07T23:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T02:25:36.000Z","uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"68da0676fdb65a87e477c86529d1a18e56ed6a09","tid":1551100,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:45:19.000Z","msg":"反修例人士提出的五大訴求中，特首林鄭月娥最終只回應了「撤回」的一點，建制派立法會議員謝偉俊今早出席電台節目時認同林鄭現時才「撤回」修例是「太少、太遲」，但他反問是否應為「少少嘅嘢」而爭拗？<span style=\"color: red;\">又稱明白部份人為了理想而做了很多事，但認為「不如醒覺做吓環保仲好啦，而家環保（問題）咁嚴峻」。</span>同場的民主黨立法會議員涂謹申反駁指，今次的修例爭議不是「小事」，強調香港的自由價值於過去幾年因DQ事件等接連被剝奪，因此觸發是次大規模的風波。<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊今早在電台節目指，林鄭突然宣佈撤回修例，旨在降溫，批評政府處理反修例示威的手法進退失據，現在才宣佈撤回是「太少、太遲」，但他同時指，若翻看林鄭過往去兩年任內政績，只犯下「一次半次政策上失誤」，<span style=\"color: red;\">反問：「林鄭政府兩年係咪真係做到大奸大惡，係咪真係做咗咁多咁嚴重傷害香港嘅嘢，導致真係不惜玉石俱焚呢？去攬炒，去破壞咁多年嘅努力？大家要問問呢個問題。」</span>謝直言，「有時的而且確佢（林鄭）真係有啲嘴臉又好、措詞又好，好多市民覺得唔啱睇、唔啱聽」，但質疑是否要因此「為咗所謂『少少嘅嘢』去爭拗呢？」<br />\n<br />\n涂謹申嚴詞反駁反修例非「小事」，指涉及香港的深層次矛盾，尤其反修例人士要求香港要有普選，因為香港的高度自治受損，舉例指過去幾年先後發生DQ風波、人大釋法、甚至驅逐外國記者等，嚴重影響香港向有的自由開放價值，「壓咗幾年嘞，香港人先至（今次）行出嚟，你估香港人想嘅咩？」"},{"pid":"16ab2fcd883d939d603d2c0f17166dc3c321deff","tid":1551100,"uid":17878,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:27:05.000Z","msg":"都唔諗下邊撚個仆街迫我地同佢攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到依一刻為止 我除左攬炒之外<br />\n<br />\n都諗唔到其他辦法制裁佢地班狗官黑警<br />\n<br />\n既然冇其他辦法<br />\n<br />\n我地唯有燃燒自己嚟同班仆街攬炒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />玉石俱焚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果攬炒係會令佢地痛不欲生嘅話<br />\n<br />\n我地就已經覺得值<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35eadfdbfe5aaba1cd7562ea6f46192c8c3e0bef","tid":1551100,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:27:42.000Z","msg":"攬炒"},{"pid":"7dc36aa9290d7074ab99258f07e35f682cb2ebca","tid":1551100,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:27:59.000Z","msg":"我代表唔到咁多人 <br />\n但我會答係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117f3f7f6b0f0875e5534a8ccf18d0e23449df22","tid":1551100,"uid":178658,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:30:26.000Z","msg":"謝偉俊係煲開老藕，可能佢想屌林奠<br />\n<br />\n咁都講得出口，奶閪奶到成個嘴都係閪汁"},{"pid":"feb020f7ad2a067879ba23ecf4fcfd1237d17b29","tid":1551100,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:31:31.000Z","msg":"咁叫政府快d滿足5大訴求再攪好環保問題<br />\n我一定支持"},{"pid":"0a6937b1d72ff0729c1de99ea7535908dc0dc053","tid":1551100,"uid":167058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:42:39.000Z","msg":"撒回再推算唔算環保？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79b9956106c895633ca648a80c1da3e66d859ca","tid":1551100,"uid":28435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:45:41.000Z","msg":"會唔會有環保膠中計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d42341ea218d9a936188f5386572ef9533afccda","tid":1551100,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:47:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6496245c505dd66c24b4511cb565e4c0276d742","tid":1551100,"uid":272580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:52:48.000Z","msg":"選我入返立法會咪最大環保囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ec3e1c24eb86d7f4cdc9929e5fcaccb0190789","tid":1551100,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d42341ea218d9a936188f5386572ef9533afccda","tid":1551100,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:47:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:01:59.000Z","msg":"文盲？<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>建制派立法會議員謝偉俊今早出席電台節目時認同林鄭現時才「撤回」修例是「太少、太遲」，但<span style=\"color: red;\">他反問是否應為「少少嘅嘢」而爭拗？</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e9924aab5de477836241293b81ae364187362237","tid":1551100,"uid":101481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:07:12.000Z","msg":"dom議員落垃圾桶"},{"pid":"11b7a2c0328b1cf3f8a57749f864e7bb525a0f94","tid":1551100,"uid":133886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:08:36.000Z","msg":"垃圾會議員?"},{"pid":"772a93996943387fc3d58435f9eb0092da06960b","tid":1551100,"uid":42740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:31:34.000Z","msg":"兩件事有沖突咩<br />\n最唔環保咪支國 你唔去抗議"},{"pid":"b63c52f9817baa24760ed6fe973c4c65fd48cf5b","tid":1551100,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:33:49.000Z","msg":"掟佢去亞馬遜救火啦"},{"pid":"5af88fd5c3d9f0c724c609331d01d2797b3248b5","tid":1551100,"uid":185121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢啲&quot;少少嘢&quot;都搞唔到, 會搞到環保?<br />\n唔好忘記搞唔掂環保其中一個重大原因係因為政府無能先得㗎。"},{"pid":"9f1427b4413f80aa7e42f0da839324a57d219c89","tid":1551100,"uid":97398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:55:35.000Z","msg":"環保？ 一齊煲老藕減少食材浪費呀？"},{"pid":"46e145e269dab6c8d852a55f0efd855d33d2300a","tid":1551100,"uid":265739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:55:59.000Z","msg":"你返屋企慰下妻先"},{"pid":"846bd894795ddde7fe8afe030111c2d613b6d3c2","tid":1551100,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:01:02.000Z","msg":"唔帶套？"},{"pid":"2000c4380f3aaacd6872fbbd8da316db5663ef5f","tid":1551100,"uid":88725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:03:21.000Z","msg":"我至撚憎環保屌你老母"},{"pid":"5de89073ce656fa4c279342ceabd1d1587a6585a","tid":1551100,"uid":7255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:08:21.000Z","msg":"環保都係政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n空氣污染已經關環保事 但政府乜柒都冇做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇腦仲衝出嚟柒"},{"pid":"4672d08588aceb7806150b2a217171272c93a926","tid":1551100,"uid":266342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:08:43.000Z","msg":"雖然我係一個會垃圾分類既人。<br />\n但最憎，係環保撚<br />\n成日籍支持環保扮好人去揾著數"},{"pid":"49c2fa6130eaeff569e5e5d3cd5e342a244dc59d","tid":1551100,"uid":726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:10:27.000Z","msg":"淨係DQ已經嚴重傷害香港啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f65c32684a75ee9438820ae89f521e6b74dd62","tid":1551100,"uid":276758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:13:52.000Z","msg":"咁佢又真係環保先鋒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n74歲阿婆都哽左咁多年"},{"pid":"0d310149bc3bb6556f9d04a783105d4070beb7c0","tid":1551100,"uid":39572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:20:08.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣真係好撚環保，食屎食到懵撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}